reviews.text: Soap is ok, but the noodle was not the type I like. Wonton average (very small, amd tiny, i perfer A bit fat.. ) Soya beam milk also A bit too thin

The noodle soup was quite good. I am not sure what kinds of meat was present in the dish but whatever there was seemed tasty. I was skeptical at first but later hunger pangs strut and tried this outlet by chance. Didn't hate it but wasn't anything too great. The authenticity of the place is perhaps present, but hygiene is a little questionable.
Ordered the wonton noodle soup, it's okay as expected. Also ordered a siu kau soup, but it was actually very bad compared to the wonton. So don't order it!!!
Very traditional noodle restaurant, Taste also very traditional, 50 years++, three generations, maintaining the taste.  Something you really should try.  Missed is really a lost

超老牌雲舌面店👍
話係米芝蓮店，雲吞及水餃水準之下，差，差，差．出名的生麵可能很多人不合口味，食落有渣的感覺。環境及坐位比大牌檔仲差，窄，熱，迫，唔知好去邊，食過幾次都十分失望，價錢又貴，冒名而去試，咁就成肚氣。
平靚正😘美味🤩令人 垂涎三尺
佢個麵好好食，地方都算乾淨 ，員工好勤力，好盡責，好爽快 不愧為喺一間老字號。
此家麵店，是元朗一間字号老的麵店，佢係香港算是一間傳統的麵店，佢的麵底是自家品牌製造，由以伊麵，彈牙及香實在美味，大家如經過的話，妨入內試試，價錢方面，比較中上價位，但不是好多大陸遊客光顧的，之前說過(字号老)，所以光顧的，多數是本地人，或由九龍香港其他遊人來光顧的，服務尚算ok
